627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":31914,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/09\/hijab-women-blind-men\/","url_meta":{"origin":32607,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Hijab: Women veiling themselves from men, even blind men","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 9, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Umm Salamah reported: While we were with the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, Ibn Maktum was given permission to enter. He entered and that was after the command to veil. The Prophet said, \u201cVeil yourselves from him.\u201d I said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, is he not\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":15295,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/07\/22\/haram-silver-gold-dishware\/","url_meta":{"origin":32607,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Extravagance: Silver and gold dishes, cutlery forbidden","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 22, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Umm Salamah reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever drinks from a vessel of gold or silver, surely he has only filled his belly with the fire of Hell.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 5634, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 2065 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi (authenticity agreed upon) according to\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":24963,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/06\/05\/dua-affirm-hearts-deen\/","url_meta":{"origin":32607,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Guidance: O Allah, affirm our hearts upon Your religion","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 5, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Umm Salamah reported: \u00a0I said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, how often you supplicate saying: O Turner of the hearts, keep my heart firm upon Your religion.\u201d The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cO Umm Salamah, there is no human but that his heart is between\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":18535,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/03\/16\/angels-bless-dua-sick\/","url_meta":{"origin":32607,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Visiting: Angels bless those who visit the ill","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 16, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Umm Salamah reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhen you visit a sick or dying person, supplicate for goodness. Verily, the angels will affirm whatever you said.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 919 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064f\u0645\u0651\u0650 \u0633\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0645\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e\u062a\u0652 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context"